{"tw": {"4272540": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "戀人日常", "steam_appid": 4272540, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/38870e21820526ffa837f34826d5534c.poster.avif?t=1771299657\" width=616 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/38870e21820526ffa837f34826d5534c.webm?t=1771299657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/38870e21820526ffa837f34826d5534c.mp4?t=1771299657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在與公司合約結束後，你開始考慮搬回父母家，或至少住到離他們更近的地方。然而就在這時，從未與你交往過的前上司卻突然向你提出了結婚的請求。更讓人難以置信的是，她甚至願意在經濟上支持你，讓你不用再工作！這真的不是在做夢嗎？還是說… 這本來就是幻想世界啊…？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隨著相處加深，你發現兩人有著驚人的共同點：不僅在金錢觀上十分合拍，連喜歡的遊戲都一樣，（甚至“閨房之樂”上也頗有共鳴）… 雖然她對啤酒的熱愛明顯更勝一籌啦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >就這樣，你們倆的新婚生活正式拉開了序幕。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/9e0571285985d9be1d40b2540d185491.poster.avif?t=1771299657\" width=616 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/9e0571285985d9be1d40b2540d185491.webm?t=1771299657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/9e0571285985d9be1d40b2540d185491.mp4?t=1771299657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >戀人日常是一款以新婚夫婦的日常生活為主題，簡單且容易上手的模擬遊戲。遊戲包含兩種不同的模式：講述主角夫妻溫馨日常的劇情模式，還有可以跟妻子進行更親密、更“適合閨房之樂”的互動模式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/453904a735a97f75fd19e63c170c3a41.poster.avif?t=1771299657\" width=616 height=642 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/453904a735a97f75fd19e63c170c3a41.webm?t=1771299657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/453904a735a97f75fd19e63c170c3a41.mp4?t=1771299657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/6c24ef8829722cb045f51fb20a8c3958.poster.avif?t=1771299657\" width=616 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/6c24ef8829722cb045f51fb20a8c3958.webm?t=1771299657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/6c24ef8829722cb045f51fb20a8c3958.mp4?t=1771299657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>純愛路線</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >體驗一段突如其來的婚姻，從最初的生疏與尷尬，逐漸發展為輕鬆、穩定，並能攜手一生的伴侶關係。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>互動模式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跟你的妻子聊聊天來增進感情，又或者去觸發澀澀的互動吧。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>美術 / 動畫+配音</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作畫風走的是簡潔路線，但是也能很好地傳達角色的情感變化。遊戲裡的大部分場景有動畫演出加語音出演。 </p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/38870e21820526ffa837f34826d5534c.poster.avif?t=1771299657\" width=616 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/38870e21820526ffa837f34826d5534c.webm?t=1771299657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/38870e21820526ffa837f34826d5534c.mp4?t=1771299657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在與公司合約結束後，你開始考慮搬回父母家，或至少住到離他們更近的地方。然而就在這時，從未與你交往過的前上司卻突然向你提出了結婚的請求。更讓人難以置信的是，她甚至願意在經濟上支持你，讓你不用再工作！這真的不是在做夢嗎？還是說… 這本來就是幻想世界啊…？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隨著相處加深，你發現兩人有著驚人的共同點：不僅在金錢觀上十分合拍，連喜歡的遊戲都一樣，（甚至“閨房之樂”上也頗有共鳴）… 雖然她對啤酒的熱愛明顯更勝一籌啦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >就這樣，你們倆的新婚生活正式拉開了序幕。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/9e0571285985d9be1d40b2540d185491.poster.avif?t=1771299657\" width=616 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/9e0571285985d9be1d40b2540d185491.webm?t=1771299657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/9e0571285985d9be1d40b2540d185491.mp4?t=1771299657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >戀人日常是一款以新婚夫婦的日常生活為主題，簡單且容易上手的模擬遊戲。遊戲包含兩種不同的模式：講述主角夫妻溫馨日常的劇情模式，還有可以跟妻子進行更親密、更“適合閨房之樂”的互動模式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/453904a735a97f75fd19e63c170c3a41.poster.avif?t=1771299657\" width=616 height=642 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/453904a735a97f75fd19e63c170c3a41.webm?t=1771299657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/453904a735a97f75fd19e63c170c3a41.mp4?t=1771299657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/6c24ef8829722cb045f51fb20a8c3958.poster.avif?t=1771299657\" width=616 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/6c24ef8829722cb045f51fb20a8c3958.webm?t=1771299657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/6c24ef8829722cb045f51fb20a8c3958.mp4?t=1771299657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>純愛路線</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >體驗一段突如其來的婚姻，從最初的生疏與尷尬，逐漸發展為輕鬆、穩定，並能攜手一生的伴侶關係。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>互動模式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跟你的妻子聊聊天來增進感情，又或者去觸發澀澀的互動吧。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>美術 / 動畫+配音</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作畫風走的是簡潔路線，但是也能很好地傳達角色的情感變化。遊戲裡的大部分場景有動畫演出加語音出演。 </p>", "short_description": "你將扮演蒼太，在這款溫馨的戀愛模擬中和自己的上司開始了同居生活。某天，她突然向你提出了結婚的請求，儘管你們幾乎從未正式約會過，你還是答應了下來。令人驚訝的是，這段看似倉促的婚姻卻進展得異常順利，接下來要做的就是，倆人一起度過平凡卻幸福的每一天。", "supported_languages": "英文, 日文<strong>*</strong>, 簡體中文, 繁體中文<br><strong>*</strong>具備完整音效支援的語言", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/f6c1eec788fe27c9092045b95d005fe67ea2e1c2/header_tchinese.jpg?t=1771299657", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/7f10322e09d006d39b094384a1788aa4ff90d1dd/capsule_231x87_tchinese.jpg?t=1771299657", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/7f10322e09d006d39b094384a1788aa4ff90d1dd/capsule_184x69_tchinese.jpg?t=1771299657", "website": "https://saikeystudios.com", "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>作業系統 *:</strong> Windows® 7/8/8.1/10/11<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel Core2 Duo or better<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 4 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> DirectX 9/OpenGL 4.1 capable GPU<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 1 GB 可用空間</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": [], "linux_requirements": [], "legal_notice": "2026 Saikey Studios", "release_date": {"coming_soon": true, "date": "即將推出"}}}}, "us": {"4272540": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Lovers' Fun!", "steam_appid": 4272540, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/50dcdf3980c7a59dc1884e0b86cde0ac.poster.avif?t=1771299657\" width=616 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/50dcdf3980c7a59dc1884e0b86cde0ac.webm?t=1771299657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/50dcdf3980c7a59dc1884e0b86cde0ac.mp4?t=1771299657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After your contract with the company ends, you start considering moving back to your parents' place, or at least somewhere nearby. But out of the blue, your former boss proposes marriage even though you've never dated. To your surprise, she's even prepared to financially support you so you don't have to work anymore! Is this real life? Or is-- wait, this is fantasy...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's surprising how much the two of you have in common. Not only are you financially compatible, but you also enjoy the same games (and possibly the same bedroom &quot;interests&quot; as well)... though she definitely loves beer more than you do. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And just like that, your new life as a married couple begins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/44585d2f2793edf60814acb95da163e7.poster.avif?t=1771299657\" width=616 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/44585d2f2793edf60814acb95da163e7.webm?t=1771299657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/44585d2f2793edf60814acb95da163e7.mp4?t=1771299657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lovers' Fun is a simple simulation game tackling on the daily life of a newly wed couple. It offers two distinct modes: a story mode that follows the heartwarming daily life of our protagonists, and a more playful mode where you can chat with your wife before you do more... &quot;bedroom appropriate&quot; activities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/c833b23d51a4155d1aa9effd2f9d445e.poster.avif?t=1771299657\" width=616 height=642 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/c833b23d51a4155d1aa9effd2f9d445e.webm?t=1771299657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/c833b23d51a4155d1aa9effd2f9d445e.mp4?t=1771299657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/cc98853dda5eb6f439f175df575d35f4.poster.avif?t=1771299657\" width=616 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/cc98853dda5eb6f439f175df575d35f4.webm?t=1771299657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/cc98853dda5eb6f439f175df575d35f4.mp4?t=1771299657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Vanilla</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as your spontaneous marriage develops from awkward into a chill life-long partnership.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Playful Interactions</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interact with your wife by either talking to her, or triggering naughty advances.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Art / Animated + Voiced</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The art is simple, yet is able to convey the emotions well. Most of the scenes are also animated and voiced.</p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/50dcdf3980c7a59dc1884e0b86cde0ac.poster.avif?t=1771299657\" width=616 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/50dcdf3980c7a59dc1884e0b86cde0ac.webm?t=1771299657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/50dcdf3980c7a59dc1884e0b86cde0ac.mp4?t=1771299657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After your contract with the company ends, you start considering moving back to your parents' place, or at least somewhere nearby. But out of the blue, your former boss proposes marriage even though you've never dated. To your surprise, she's even prepared to financially support you so you don't have to work anymore! Is this real life? Or is-- wait, this is fantasy...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's surprising how much the two of you have in common. Not only are you financially compatible, but you also enjoy the same games (and possibly the same bedroom &quot;interests&quot; as well)... though she definitely loves beer more than you do. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And just like that, your new life as a married couple begins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/44585d2f2793edf60814acb95da163e7.poster.avif?t=1771299657\" width=616 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/44585d2f2793edf60814acb95da163e7.webm?t=1771299657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/44585d2f2793edf60814acb95da163e7.mp4?t=1771299657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lovers' Fun is a simple simulation game tackling on the daily life of a newly wed couple. It offers two distinct modes: a story mode that follows the heartwarming daily life of our protagonists, and a more playful mode where you can chat with your wife before you do more... &quot;bedroom appropriate&quot; activities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/c833b23d51a4155d1aa9effd2f9d445e.poster.avif?t=1771299657\" width=616 height=642 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/c833b23d51a4155d1aa9effd2f9d445e.webm?t=1771299657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/c833b23d51a4155d1aa9effd2f9d445e.mp4?t=1771299657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/cc98853dda5eb6f439f175df575d35f4.poster.avif?t=1771299657\" width=616 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/cc98853dda5eb6f439f175df575d35f4.webm?t=1771299657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/extras/cc98853dda5eb6f439f175df575d35f4.mp4?t=1771299657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Vanilla</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as your spontaneous marriage develops from awkward into a chill life-long partnership.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Playful Interactions</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interact with your wife by either talking to her, or triggering naughty advances.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Art / Animated + Voiced</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The art is simple, yet is able to convey the emotions well. Most of the scenes are also animated and voiced.</p>", "short_description": "Play as Souta in this heart-warming simulation game where you live with your boss that suddenly proposed to you. You accept the marriage, even though you've spent zero seconds dating each other, but everything actually turns out well. All that's left to do is get to know her better and enjoy life.", "supported_languages": "English, Japanese<strong>*</strong>, Simplified Chinese, Traditional Chinese<br><strong>*</strong>languages with full audio support", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/51c9b6436be3523e16d6d6640c61a5630cadc1ec/header.jpg?t=1771299657", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/6143d7e7c7a45e2c23aaf8fd3092d8d276618b54/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1771299657", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4272540/6143d7e7c7a45e2c23aaf8fd3092d8d276618b54/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1771299657", "website": "https://saikeystudios.com", "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS *:</strong> Windows® 7/8/8.1/10/11<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Intel Core2 Duo or better<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 4 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> DirectX 9/OpenGL 4.1 capable GPU<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 1 GB available space</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": [], "linux_requirements": [], "legal_notice": "2026 Saikey Studios", "release_date": {"coming_soon": true, "date": "Coming soon"}}}}, "fetched_at": "2026-04-22T04:55:42Z"}